563
00:50:44,660 --> 00:50:48,570
♫ I will be here ♫​

564
00:50:48,570 --> 00:50:51,610
Bread that Myeong Hee likes.

565
00:50:51,610 --> 00:50:52,890
Hee Tae.

566
00:50:52,890 --> 00:50:54,420
Why? Let's get it.

567
00:50:54,420 --> 00:50:59,570
