568
00:50:59,570 --> 00:51:02,260
♫ I will always  ♫​

569
00:51:02,260 --> 00:51:07,660
♫ laugh with you ♫​

570
00:51:07,660 --> 00:51:14,020
♫ I know, that's how we become one ♫​

571
00:51:17,070 --> 00:51:18,790
What are you doing?

572
00:51:18,790 --> 00:51:21,680
